data.description: *** Assumable Mortgage at 5.75% *** Welcome to this impeccably kept, open-concept residence in the secure, gated SEDELLA community. The inviting front porch and courtyard set the stage for this family-friendly home. Inside, the large kitchen overlooks a generous backyard with a pristine pool(Solar Heater) and RV parking. With multiple built-ins, an office, a den, and a large living room, space is abundant. The home offers a flexible layout with a potential for four bedrooms, but currently features an extra living area. Residents enjoy community amenities such as basketball and volleyball courts and are conveniently located near top-rated schools and new shopping centers. A perfect blend of luxury and functionality awaits.
